      "zh": "一款支持高度定制的模块化插板胸挂，最大限度保证穿戴者在战斗中的舒适度，由 Spiritus Systems 公司设计制造。狼灰色版本。便利的布局让使用者能够轻松携带备用弹药以及其他必要的装备，同时不会影响自由行动。",
      "en": "A highly customizable modular plate carrier by Spiritus Systems, built for maximum comfort in combat. Wolf Grey version. This setup allows full freedom of movement while providing an ergonomic layout for ammunition and essential gear."
